No-Trading/Missing-Day Handling:
- Baseline uses a complete daily UTC calendar from start_date to end_date.
- Dates without eligible signals or active positions are retained with zero portfolio return and zero exposure.
- Individual symbol missing returns are treated as zero for that symbol and logged as anomalies.

Schemas:
- prices_daily.parquet
  - date: datetime64[ns]; unit=UTC calendar date
  - symbol: string; unit=crypto symbol from local DB
  - open: float64; unit=USDT
  - high: float64; unit=USDT
  - low: float64; unit=USDT
  - close: float64; unit=USDT
  - volume: float64; unit=base asset contracts/coins
  - quote_volume: float64; unit=USDT proxy, close * volume
- universe_membership.parquet
  - date: datetime64[ns]; unit=UTC calendar date
  - symbol: string; unit=Bybit perpetual symbol
  - is_member: bool; unit=true rows only; absent rows are false
- 20260513_run003_baseline.csv
  - date: datetime64[ns]; unit=UTC calendar date
  - portfolio_return: float64; unit=decimal daily return
  - benchmark_return: float64; unit=decimal daily return
  - gross_exposure: float64; unit=sum(abs(weights))
  - net_exposure: float64; unit=sum(weights)
  - turnover: float64; unit=sum(abs(delta weight)) on effective date
  - n_longs: int64; unit=active long positions
  - n_shorts: int64; unit=active short positions
- 20260513_run003_positions.parquet
  - date: datetime64[ns]; unit=UTC calendar date
  - decision_date: datetime64[ns]; unit=date when weights were decided
  - effective_date: datetime64[ns]; unit=date when weights became active
  - symbol: string; unit=Bybit perpetual symbol
  - weight: float64; unit=portfolio weight
  - signal_rank: int64; unit=1 is strongest momentum
  - signal_value: float64; unit=ranking score used for this symbol
  - is_member: bool; unit=PIT universe membership on the position date
- 20260513_run003_stats.json
  - ir: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for ir_full
  - sharpe: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for sharpe_full
  - sortino: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for sortino_full
  - max_dd: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for max_dd_full
  - calmar: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for calmar_full
  - turnover_annual: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for turnover_annual_full
  - hit_rate: float64; unit=legacy full-period alias for hit_rate_full
  - ir_full: float64; unit=full-period annualized active return / active volatility
  - ir_active: float64; unit=active-period annualized active return / active volatility
  - sharpe_full: float64; unit=full-period annualized mean portfolio return / volatility
  - sharpe_active: float64; unit=active-period annualized mean portfolio return / volatility
  - sortino_full: float64; unit=full-period annualized mean portfolio return / downside volatility
  - sortino_active: float64; unit=active-period annualized mean portfolio return / downside volatility
  - max_dd_full: float64; unit=full-period decimal drawdown
  - max_dd_active: float64; unit=active-period decimal drawdown
  - calmar_full: float64; unit=full-period CAGR / abs(max drawdown)
  - calmar_active: float64; unit=active-period CAGR / abs(max drawdown)
  - turnover_annual_full: float64; unit=full-period sum daily turnover / elapsed years
  - turnover_annual_active: float64; unit=active-period sum daily turnover / elapsed years
  - hit_rate_full: float64; unit=full-period share of days with positive portfolio return
  - hit_rate_active: float64; unit=active-period share of days with positive portfolio return
